FRAMING UR THOUGHTS



1.have sth 2 say & think it through

2. 4 maximal efficiency,plan ur writing projects.
  Try nonlinear outlining.

3.order ur material in a logical sequence.
  Present facts chronologically, keep related material together.

4 divide the document into sections, and sections into subparts as needed.
  Use informative headings.